<br>
At one point in my early career, some of my pets required Lapis to cast, instead of Malachite.  It really bugged me, cuz they were *expensive*, and then the pets went back to Malachite awhile later and I was like WTF?? :)<br>
<br>
I remember the first time that my guild, along with a couple of others, took down Vox for the very first time.  A GM was there to witness it and broadcasted a serverwide message congradulating us. <br>
